  "title": "Junior Sales Marketing Associates (Training provided)",
  "description": "<p>We’re an <strong>international outsourced sales and marketing company</strong>, partnering with brands across multiple industries to drive growth through high-impact, people-focused campaigns.</p><p>Not sure what’s next after graduating or ORD? Maybe you’re looking for something hands-on, fun, and full of growth. If that’s you — keep reading.<br /><br />Experience? <strong>Not needed.</strong> Enthusiasm? <strong>Yes, please.</strong><br /><br /><br /><strong>What You’ll Get to Do:</strong><br />🎡 Be part of exciting events and roadshows<br />🗣 Engage with people daily and sharpen your communication skills<br />💼 Learn new skills in a supportive, energetic team environment<br />🌍 Represent global brands and create strong, lasting impressions<br /><br /><br /><strong>What You’ll Get in Return:</strong><br />💰 Weekly payouts with unlimited commission<br />🎁 Extra incentives for strong performance<br />📚 Skill-building workshops and hands-on training<br />🚀 Clear leadership pathways if you want to advance<br />✈️ Travel opportunities to broaden your exposure<br /><br /><br />Bring your energy — we’ll provide the training.<br />If you’re ready to start a fresh chapter, reach out and apply. There’s nothing to lose.</p>",
